version_description: Account Details Bug Fix, Validation to check Mobile Number is registered to access M-Connect Plus.

1. Bharat QR – Interoperable payment service by scanning Bharat QR
2. Debit card Hotlisting
3. Refresh operative accounts
4. Demo of Mconnect plus application
5. Multilingual – Hindi, English, Gujarathi
6. Bug fixes and improvements

New features included –
1. BBPS (Bharat Bill Payment System)
2. Account Statement
3. TDS Certificate
4. Interest Certificate
5. FD & RD opening/View Receipts and Interest Rates
6. Modified Branch & ATM Locator including fetching nearby places.
7. Bug Fixes(Password cannot be blank issue during registration etc.)
